# SkillPathForge AI — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your real values
# NEVER commit .env — only commit .env.example

# Claude API
CLAUDE_API_KEY=your_claude_api_key_here

# Server
BACKEND_PORT=8000
FRONTEND_PORT=3000
ENVIRONMENT=development
APP_NAME=SkillPathForge-AI
```

---

### The rule is simple
```
.env.example   → COMMIT ✓   (template, no real values)
.env           → NEVER  ✗   (real API keys, in .gitignore)